creator: Ali Kurnaz
descriptionHtml:
Have you tried to quit smoking suddenly but failed? Now you want to try to reduce? Thanks to Smokeless, you can reduce or quit smoking until the date you set. You do not have to keep in mind when to smoke the next cigarette. The application will do this for you.

By creating a program in the application, you choose the number of cigarettes you smoke, the number you target and how long you want to reduce. It shows how soon you should smoke the next cigarette by using its special algorithm for reduction. This interval will increase over time. Thus, your smoking frequency will decrease. Your cigarettes accumulate when you are not smoking. When you smoke, you use the accumulated cigarettes by pressing button "I smoked!". You can also see the elapsed time and how much you have decreased.

You will see how easily you can reduce smoking if you stick to the program you created.

Have you tried to quit smoking suddenly but failed? Now you want to try to reduce? Thanks to Smokeless, you can reduce or quit smoking until the date you set. You do not have to keep in mind when to smoke the next cigarette. The application will do this for you.

By creating a program in the application, you choose the number of cigarettes you smoke, the number you target and how long you want to reduce. It shows how soon you should smoke the next cigarette by using its special algorithm for reduction. This interval will increase over time. Thus, your smoking frequency will decrease. Your cigarettes accumulate when you are not smoking. When you smoke, you use the accumulated cigarettes by pressing button "I smoked!". You can also see the elapsed time and how much you have decreased.

You will see how easily you can reduce smoking if you stick to the program you created.
descriptionShort: Smokeless is an application that helps you quit by reducing smoking

creator: Ali Kurnaz
descriptionHtml:
Take control of your smoking habits and work towards a healthier lifestyle!

Struggling to quit smoking or looking to reduce the number of cigarettes you consume daily? This no smoking tracker is designed to help you monitor, analyse, and gradually cut down on your smoking habits with an intuitive system that encourages healthier choices. Whether you want to track your consumption, set goals, or stay motivated, this app supports you every step of the way.

How It Works

Each time you smoke, simply tap the button to log it. The app records your smoking patterns and presents detailed statistics, allowing you to understand your habits better. With three structured programmes – Linear Descending, Fixed Interval, and Minimum Interval – you can choose a tailored approach to cutting back.

Key Features:

✔ Cigarette tracker – Keep a precise count of every cigarette you smoke
✔ Nicotine free counter – Track smoke-free days and celebrate milestones ✔ Quitting smoking app – A structured way to quit smoking gradually
✔ Healthier choices – Reduce and replace smoking with better habits
✔ Statistics & insights – Get detailed analytics about your smoking patterns ✔ Support & motivation – Stay on track with reminders and progress tracking
✔ Vaping alternative – Apply the same reduction techniques to vaping

Why Use This App?

This app is more than just a cigarette app – it’s a quit bad habits app that helps you develop discipline and control over your smoking patterns. Whether you’re cutting back on vaping or quitting altogether, this tool provides essential support to guide you towards success.

With structured data, easy-to-read graphs, and clear statistics, you’ll be able to monitor your progress and see tangible improvements. Every step you take towards reducing your nicotine intake is a step towards a healthier future!

Designed for Every Smoker

● If you’re looking for a quitting smoking app, this provides structured plans to help you succeed.
● If you want a no smoking tracker, this helps you stay accountable.
● If you aim to transition to a nicotine free counter, this app tracks your progress seamlessly.
● If you use vaping, this app can assist in controlling your usage.

Start Your Journey Today!

Take control of your health, track your smoking, and move towards a healthier life. Download now and make the change you’ve been thinking about!
descriptionShort: Get support for cigarette cessation, track statistics, and live a healthier life
